==References==

==Dominican Navy==

The ''Citrus'' was initially transferred to the [[Mexican Navy]], but delivery was refused in February 1995. The ''Citrus'' was transferred to the [[Dominican Navy]] on 16 September 1995, and renamed ''Almirante Juan Alejandro Acosta'' (C-456). It has been rearmed with a 102 mm 45 caliber [[Dual purpose gun|DP gun]], two single [[Oerlikon 20 mm cannon]]s, and four [[7.62 mm]] [[M60 machine gun]]s.<ref name=citrus/><ref name =combat/>

